peopleAlsoAsk.question: Who is Phil Prentice?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: Wildlife Artist Phil Prentice was born in 1930 in Muncie Indiana. At the age of 12 he received a scholarship at the Dayton Art Institute to study under Cartoonist Al Capp and Milton Caniff. He went on to study in 1950 at the Pratt Art Institute, Brooklyn, New York.
